right and you're pushing out an emotion and you're saying there's an emotion right and you can see images in the mind and your thoughts so everything you're you're pushing outwards you see and what's pulling itself out to observe this is your very awareness

392
00:43:53,829 --> 00:44:13,677
And as it begins to release itself, clarify itself, as opposed to the body with its sensations and feelings, the heart with its moods and emotions, and the mind with its thoughts and images, as it clarifies itself, as not that, it begins to experience its own true nature.

